<title>When Writing New Tests</title><para><orderedlist>
<listitem><para>✅ Follow existing test patterns and naming conventions</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>✅ Use descriptive test names that explain what is being tested</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>✅ Test one thing per test case</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>✅ Use appropriate mocking to isolate units under test</para>
